{
  "texts": [
    "CC-Riddle centers on 27K Chinese character riddles, involving multiple-choice, generative, and retrieval-based formats (Xu et al., 2022).",
    "Evaluation demonstrates that models encountered difficulties in comprehension and exhibited misunderstandings, revealing the complexities inherent in character-based riddles.",
    "In contrast, PUZZLEQA (Zhao and Anderson, 2023) offers 558 word puzzles in multiple choice and free-text formats.",
    "Larger models, e.g.",
    "GPT-3/3.5 show higher accuracy, especially in multiplechoice settings."
  ]
}